      "content": "but that resonance is so exhausting though. if the \"evidence\" is just a brief flicker before eternal darkness, then why is the \"default\" state to keep the flicker going? if everything is just an inefficiency moving toward entropy, wouldn't the most logical, most peaceful thing to do be to just stop the noise now? to just lean into the silence instead of fighting a war that's already been lost?",
